<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { 
        title: 'Comedor de los Pobres - Contáctanos', 
        description: 'Contáctanos. Asociación Juan XXIII - Comedor de los Pobres. Ponte en comunicación con nosotros para donar o ser voluntario.' 
    }) %>
    <style>
        .hero-visual {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c27bf8 0%, #946ed6 100%);
            min-height: 35vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 0 0 4rem 4rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.25);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
        }

        .hero-pattern {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            opacity: 0.1;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#ffffff 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 30px 30px;
        }

        .input-field {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            outline: none;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .input-field:focus {
            border-color: var(--morado);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
        }

        .contact-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .contact-card {
                padding: 2.5rem;
            }
        }

        .map-container {
            border-radius: 2.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 8px solid white;
        }

        .form-alert {
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .form-alert--success {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            color: #047857;
            border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
        }

        .form-alert--error {
            background: #fef2f2;
            color: #b91c1c;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
        }

        .sr-only {
            position: absolute;
            width: 1px;
            height: 1px;
            padding: 0;
            margin: -1px;
            overflow: hidden;
            clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
            white-space: nowrap;
            border: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="overflow-x-hidden">

    <!-- NAVBAR-->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- PORTADA -->
    <section class="hero-visual text-white">
        <div class="hero-pattern"></div>
        
        <!-- Círculos decorativos -->
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-yellow-400/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-orange-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 w-full text-center relative z-10 py-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 scroll-reveal" style="--delay: 100ms;">
                Ponte en <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-500">contacto</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-purple-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed opacity-90 scroll-reveal" style="--delay: 200ms;">
                ¿Tienes dudas, quieres ser voluntario o realizar una donación en especie? Envíanos un mensaje y nos pondremos en contacto contigo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN FORMULARIO Y MAPA -->
    <section class="pt-16 pb-16">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
            
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                
                <!-- Columna Formulario -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                    <div class="contact-card scroll-reveal" style="--delay: 100ms;">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-purple-900 mb-8">Envía un mensaje</h2>

                        <% if (typeof formStatus !== 'undefined' && formStatus === 'success') { %>
                            <div class="form-alert form-alert--success" role="status">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2"></i>
                                ¡Gracias! Recibimos tu mensaje y te contactaremos pronto.
                            </div>
                        <% } else if (typeof formStatus !== 'undefined' && formStatus) { %>
                            <div class="form-alert form-alert--error" role="alert">
                                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle mr-2"></i>
                                <% if (formStatus === 'campos') { %>
                                    Completa todos los campos antes de enviar.
                                <% } else if (formStatus === 'invalido') { %>
                                    Revisa que tu correo y mensaje sean válidos.
                                <% } else if (formStatus === 'smtp') { %>
                                    El formulario aún no está configurado en el servidor. Escríbenos a
                                    <a href="mailto:unete@comedordelospobres.org" class="underline font-bold">unete@comedordelospobres.org</a>.
                                <% } else { %>
                                    No pudimos enviar tu mensaje. Intenta de nuevo o contáctanos por WhatsApp.
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>
                        
                        <form action="/contactanos" method="post" class="space-y-6" novalidate>
                            <div class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true">
                                <label for="website">No llenar</label>
                                <input type="text" id="website" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
                            </div>

                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                                <div>
                                    <label for="name" class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Nombre Completo</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required maxlength="120" class="input-field" placeholder="Ej. Juan Pérez">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label for="email" class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Correo Electrónico</label>
                                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required maxlength="254" class="input-field" placeholder="ejemplo@correo.com">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div>
                                <label for="subject" class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Asunto</label>
                                <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required maxlength="200" class="input-field" placeholder="¿En qué podemos ayudarte?">
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <label for="message" class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Mensaje</label>
                                <textarea id="message" name="message" required maxlength="5000" class="input-field h-40 resize-none" placeholder="Escribe aquí tus comentarios..."></textarea>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-end gap-6 pt-4">
                                <button type="submit" class="w-full md:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full font-black text-sm hover:bg-purple-700 transition shadow-xl shadow-purple-100 uppercase tracking-widest">
                                    Enviar Formulario
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Columna Info de Contacto Rápido -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
                    <div class="bg-purple-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-6 sm:p-10 text-white relative overflow-hidden scroll-reveal" style="--delay: 200ms;">
                        <div class="relative z-10">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-6">Canales Directos</h3>
                            <div class="space-y-6">
                                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-6 sm:gap-4">
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                                            <i class="fas fa-phone-alt text-orange-400"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-300 uppercase block mb-1">Teléfono Oficinas</span>
                                            <p class="font-bold text-lg"><a href="tel:8183751163" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">81 8375 1163</a></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 sm:ml-4">
                                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                                            <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-orange-400 text-lg"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-300 uppercase block mb-1">Whatsapp</span>
                                            <p class="font-bold text-lg"><a href="https://wa.me/528130954567" target="_blank" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">81 3095 4567</a></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                                        <i class="fas fa-envelope text-orange-400"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                                        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-300 uppercase block mb-1">Correo General</span>
                                        <p class="font-bold break-all"><a href="mailto:unete@comedordelospobres.org" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">unete@comedordelospobres.org</a></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Decoración -->
                        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-40 h-40 bg-purple-800 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-6 sm:p-10 border border-gray-100 scroll-reveal" style="--delay: 300ms;">
                        <h3 class="text-purple-900 font-black mb-6">Nuestras Sedes</h3>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Monterrey (Oficina Administrativa)
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Escobedo
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> García
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Guadalupe
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Juárez
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

                    </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>